      (adj-punchIn-РёЋ (fst i) (fst c))

  -- Face shift: by induction on gap d where suc(fst i) + d = fst j.
  -- Base: d=0, adjacent faces agree pointwise (¤Ѓ(i) = ¤Ѓ(j) bridges the gap).
  -- Step: define ¤Ѓ' = ¤Ѓ Рѕў swap(i, i+1). Then:
  --   face i of ¤Ѓ = face (i+1) of ¤Ѓ'  [punchIn-swap identity]
  --   face j of ¤Ѓ' = (face j of ¤Ѓ) Рѕў swap  [swap-punchIn commutation]
